00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:30,612
[ grunts ]

271
00:09:30,695 --> 00:09:32,363
You're pathetic!

272
00:09:32,447 --> 00:09:34,032
[ hisses ]

273
00:09:34,115 --> 00:09:36,701
Get ready for an uppercut, you dog!

274
00:09:36,785 --> 00:09:39,037
Make me.

275
00:09:39,120 --> 00:09:41,206
[ laughs evilly ]

276
00:09:41,289 --> 00:09:43,458
Blah, blah!

277
00:09:43,541 --> 00:09:46,044
Blah!

278
00:09:46,127 --> 00:09:48,463
l...
got to help my buddy!

279
00:09:48,546 --> 00:09:49,756
Your blood is mine!

280
00:09:49,839 --> 00:09:52,217
[ warbling loudly ]

281
00:09:52,300 --> 00:09:56,638
[ grunting ]

282
00:09:56,721 --> 00:10:00,558
- [ gasps ]
- Uh-oh.

283
00:10:00,642 --> 00:10:01,559
[ laughs evilly ]

284
00:10:01,643 --> 00:10:03,978
[ screams ]

285
00:10:04,062 --> 00:10:05,522
[ breathing heavily ]

286
00:10:05,605 --> 00:10:06,981
[ screams ]

287
00:10:07,065 --> 00:10:08,191
Ow!

288
00:10:08,274 --> 00:10:10,527
That... actually hurt, Finn.

289
00:10:10,610 --> 00:10:13,363
[ laughs evilly ]

290
00:10:13,446 --> 00:10:16,991
[ shrieks ]

291
00:10:17,075 --> 00:10:19,994
[ laughs ]
Mwah!

292
00:10:20,078 --> 00:10:21,830
W-Why you didn't just kill me?

293
00:10:21,913 --> 00:10:23,456
'Cause that was fun!

294
00:10:23,540 --> 00:10:25,959
Whew, | haven't fought
like that in years.

295
00:10:26,042 --> 00:10:27,210
Thanks, Finn.

296
00:10:27,293 --> 00:10:28,628
Finn.

297
00:10:28,711 --> 00:10:29,671
A-Aren't you dead?

298
00:10:29,754 --> 00:10:31,548
Nah, before she bit me, | used my powers

299
00:10:31,631 --> 00:10:34,300
to shrink all my guts and blood
over to my thumb, see?

300
00:10:34,384 --> 00:10:35,718
[ clears throat ]

301
00:10:35,802 --> 00:10:37,679
You two are pretty hard core.

302
00:10:37,762 --> 00:10:39,139
| can appreciate that.

303
00:10:39,222 --> 00:10:44,519
So... so does that mean
we can have our old house back?

304
00:10:44,602 --> 00:10:46,062
Yeah, keep it...

305
00:10:46,146 --> 00:10:48,148
as a gift from me!

306
00:10:48,231 --> 00:10:49,691
Blah!

307
00:10:49,774 --> 00:10:50,567
[ both screaming ]

308
00:10:50,650 --> 00:10:52,944
[ laughs ]

309
00:10:53,027 --> 00:10:55,029
BOTH:
Yeah! Huh?

310
00:10:55,113 --> 00:10:57,740
[ all croaking ]

311
00:10:57,824 --> 00:11:00,118
[ all warbling ]

312
00:11:00,201 --> 00:11:01,661
Did you guys get on the bed?

313
00:11:01,744 --> 00:11:03,997
| told you, you're not allowed!

314
00:11:04,080 --> 00:11:05,707
MAN:
Oh, hey, guys.

315
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:07,000
BOTH:
Huh?

316
00:11:07,083 --> 00:11:10,003
Come here, friends. Hug me.

317
00:11:10,086 --> 00:11:11,838
[ warbling ]

318
00:11:11,921 --> 00:11:14,841
Oh, yeah. Hug me.

319
00:11:14,924 --> 00:11:17,677
[ warbling ]

320
00:11:19,179 --> 00:11:23,391
» Come along with me »

321
00:11:23,474 --> 00:11:27,395
2 And the butterflies and bees

322
00:11:27,478 --> 00:11:31,399
» We can wander through the forest J»

323
00:11:31,482 --> 00:11:35,570
> And do so as we please >

324
00:11:35,653 --> 00:11:39,407
» Come along with me »

325
00:11:39,490 --> 00:11:43,161
D To a cliff under a tree »

